{"tid":1147420,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4/Xbox One/PC]《Monster Hunter:World》超大型擴張DLC「Iceborne」討論區","createTime":"2019-05-09T23:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T12:40:45.000Z","uid":75050,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e1cbf91a052c457d183a0e5d392f2f5999f33ace","tid":1147420,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T23:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pFmKBs2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpFmKBs2.jpg&h=75a4c62b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《魔物獵人:世界》「Iceborne」新宣傳影片公開，新魔物登場，迅龍正式亮相，<span style=\"color: red;\">該DLC將於9月6日在PS4/Xbox One平台推出，PC則稍晚一些</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z-JMHHJbA28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dz-JMHHJbA28&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=4a705129\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z-JMHHJbA28</a><br />\n<br />\n《魔物獵人 世界》超大型擴張DLC「Iceborne」共新增魔物：「古龍冰咒龍」「猛牛龍」、「冰魚龍」、「迅龍」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>冰呪龍</strong><br />\n冰呪龍是此次DLC的主題怪物，相關的內容目前沒有釋出太多，更多需要等後續公開。 ​​​<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6bq5iZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6bq5iZ.jpg&h=6fad7e84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>猛牛龍</strong><br />\n擁有一對壓倒性的巨角，會利用周圍的環境進行攻擊以及猛衝，猛牛龍屬於溫順性怪物，平時不會主動攻擊獵人。 ​​​​<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOT5kSo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOT5kSo.jpg&h=372c574e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>冰魚龍</strong><br />\n和大多數魚龍種一樣，冰魚龍會在「水（雪）」中發動突然襲擊攻擊獵人。牠和猛牛龍將有地盤爭奪，會主動攻擊波波。 ​​​​<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dV4j9LT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdV4j9LT.jpg&h=b1d83b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>迅龍</strong><br />\n在此次《世界》中登場的迅龍，將延續以往的攻擊技巧和一些令人懷念的攻擊方式，並根據遊戲的設計加入一些全新的戰鬥方式、生態以及地盤爭奪等。 ​​​​<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8QaWsxt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8QaWsxt.jpg&h=85402852&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30df44d24fdbeeb766e429826ba7b46a48e93e25","tid":1147420,"uid":40216,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:06:30.000Z","msg":"無轟龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f9d28f68b7682123933a6df22ad9e94c6f0e14","tid":1147420,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:19:17.000Z","msg":"早左出?"},{"pid":"2f734b6bcd0c09accca4083b8b13dbcb863b3926","tid":1147420,"uid":190617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30df44d24fdbeeb766e429826ba7b46a48e93e25","tid":1147420,"uid":40216,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:06:30.000Z","msg":"無轟龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:21:31.000Z","msg":"應該有, PV尾段似佢叫"},{"pid":"b84701d500a36e44a7bfced428e416efccc3a9de","tid":1147420,"uid":58947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:21:37.000Z","msg":"Dklm 得4-5 隻新龍 就埋單"},{"pid":"64410a15c4668e0a3538f4eaab9e4470e5ace19a","tid":1147420,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f734b6bcd0c09accca4083b8b13dbcb863b3926","tid":1147420,"uid":190617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30df44d24fdbeeb766e429826ba7b46a48e93e25","tid":1147420,"uid":40216,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:06:30.000Z","msg":"無轟龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:21:31.000Z","msg":"應該有, PV尾段似佢叫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:22:37.000Z","msg":"唔係迅龍咩?"},{"pid":"89ce013cee1a6c0c607760d0650fa6a208e2b0ab","tid":1147420,"uid":190617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64410a15c4668e0a3538f4eaab9e4470e5ace19a","tid":1147420,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"